						<div class="postbody">Don't forget that the CHRRAM is banked just like CHRROM would, even if all commercial games just switch banks 0-2-4-5-6-7 in (that allow you to fully use the 8k of CHRRAM).
<br />You should bankswitch correct bank of CHRRAM into the MMC3.</div>

					
